original: Lagerlunda, Malmslätt, f. 29/11/05 å Lagerlunda, östergötl. 1., av godsäg., frih. Israel L. o. Malla Wachtmeister. G. 35 m. Barbro de Besche. Barn: Carl-Gustaf f. 35, Bleckert 37, Gunilla 42. — Agronomex. v. Alnarp 31. Fänrik v. Andra livgren :reg. 27, kapt. 42.
translated: Lagerlunda, Malmslätt, born 29/11/05 in Lagerlunda, in the county of Östergötland. First child of the landowner and nobility, Israel Lagerlöf and Malla Wachtmeister. Married in 1935 to Barbro de Besche. Children: Carl-Gustaf, born in 1935, Bleckert, born in 1937, and Gunilla, born in 1942. Graduated from the Alnarp Agricultural Institute in 1931. Appointed as an ensign in the 27th Infantry Regiment, and promoted to captain in 1942.
